    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at level 1, your hands are incredibly soft, and you enjoy kneading those you consider friendly or when you feel safe. This action resembles a calming and relaxing massage. Once per long rest, you and your allies can roll an extra chakra and hp dice on a short rest, as long as you roll at least 1 of such dice, for free but without adding their constitution modifier to them. At level 7 this allows you to roll 2 extra hp and chakra dice per long rest.</p>",
